item.title: Object help PI 317
item.dc:creator: @ljoxaa ljoxaa
item.description:
@ljoxaa wrote:

Playerassistant.java
Search,
Code:

public void removeObjects() {

if you can’t find it then search,
Code:

public int getNpcId(int id) {

You should see some methods called removeObject, Objecttoremove, and objecttoremove2 something like that, if you do not have them then under the public in get npcid add,
Code:

public void removeObject(int x, int y) {
	object(-1, x, x, 10, 10);
}

private void objectToRemove(int X, int Y) {
	object(-1, X, Y, 10, 10);
}

private void objectToRemove2(int X, int Y) {
	object(-1, X, Y, -1, 0);
}

now under those add
Code:

public void removeObjects() {

then add right under that
Code:

objectToRemove(OBJECT X, OBJECT Y);

done.
